summary.textblock: This document substitutes Channel 251C1 for Channel 251C2 at Titusville, Florida, and modifies the license for Station WGNE(FM) to specify operation on Channel 251C1, at the request of Southern Starr Limited Partnership. See 58 FR 52734, October 12, 1993. Channel 251C1 can be allotted to Titusville in compliance with the Commission's minimum distance separation requirements with a site restriction of 23.6 kilometers (14.6 miles) southeast of the community. The coordinates for Channel 251C1 at Titusville are North Latitude 28-35-00 and West Longitude 80-34-10. With this action, this proceeding is terminated.

further.textblock: Nancy J. Walls, Mass Media Bureau, (202) 634-6530.

List of Subjects in 47 CFR Part 73
Radio broadcasting Part 73 of title 47 of the Code of Federal Regulations is amended as follows:
1. The authority citation for part 73 continues to read as follows:
2. Section 73.202(b), the Table of FM Allotments under Florida, is amended by removing Channel 251C2 and by adding Channel 251C1 at Titusville.
